<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="id56959a7b-2930-11f1-a4c1-c531e6569a02"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior section 507 was renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t14/s2710">section 2710 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
